  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wizard brawler about spell drafting and beard envy, MageQuit allows up to 10 mages to battle online or locally. Beards grow longer with each kill; the wizard with the longest beard after 9 rounds wins! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1-10 players local or online, featuring crossplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70 different spells </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom bots for online or offline play </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anonymous skillbased or custom matchmaking </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spell drafting </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spell curving </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouse and keyboard support  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as teams, free for all, or 1v1 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic original sound track </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WAYS TO PLAY MAGEQUIT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play offline with a group of up to 10 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo in online quickplay or offline with bots </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online with a premade party of up to 10 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the online quickplay queue with a party of up to 5 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online with multiple players on the same PC </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/572220/extras/e8455b7897201563d41e98328fd138c7.poster.avif?t=1769902375\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/572220/extras/e8455b7897201563d41e98328fd138c7.webm?t=1769902375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/572220/extras/e8455b7897201563d41e98328fd138c7.mp4?t=1769902375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OFFICIAL TOURNAMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have semi-monthly<strong> official tournaments</strong> casted on <strong>our twitch channel</strong>! Finalists receive <strong>game keys</strong>; winners receive <strong>in-game rewards</strong>. All experience levels are welcome.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sign up <strong>in-game</strong> or with command <i>+signup</i> in <strong>our discord</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/572220/extras/ea838fd58354ab0db5ce22c5ea6c21d2.avif?t=1769902375\" width=476 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FUTURE ANNOUNCEMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Follow</strong> our new <strong>Steam Developer Page</strong> to be notified of  future releases!<br><i>It's the <strong>Bowlcut Studios</strong> link in the right panel, and seriously it's super new.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We announce things in <strong>our discord</strong> as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/572220/extras/4a8c25ca6bd024a936369af741a89224.avif?t=1769902375\" width=476 height=146 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wizard brawler about spell drafting and beard envy, MageQuit allows up to 10 mages to battle online or locally. Beards grow longer with each kill; the wizard with the longest beard after 9 rounds wins! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1-10 players local or online, featuring crossplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70 different spells </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom bots for online or offline play </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anonymous skillbased or custom matchmaking </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spell drafting </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spell curving </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouse and keyboard support  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as teams, free for all, or 1v1 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic original sound track </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WAYS TO PLAY MAGEQUIT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play offline with a group of up to 10 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo in online quickplay or offline with bots </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online with a premade party of up to 10 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the online quickplay queue with a party of up to 5 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play online with multiple players on the same PC </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/572220/extras/e8455b7897201563d41e98328fd138c7.poster.avif?t=1769902375\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass